        <item>
            <title>NVIDIA 2025 CES 黃仁勳演講透視： 老闆們留意，企業將有 7 大改變</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/07/ai-enterpise/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-enterpise</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/07/ai-enterpise/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[天恩]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 11:12:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Unwire Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
