            <title>【CES2025】AMD AI 處理器爭奪人工智能市場，提升 Copilot+ PC、遊戲體驗 Ryzen AI Max、Ryzen AI 300、Ryzen AI 200</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/07/ryzen-ai-max-ryzen-ai-300-ryzen-ai-200/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ryzen-ai-max-ryzen-ai-300-ryzen-ai-200</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/07/ryzen-ai-max-ryzen-ai-300-ryzen-ai-200/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
